/Dockerfile
.git

# partial copy of .gitignore
*.o
*.a
*.[5678iv]
*.ao
# pad's test files -- without these, a leftover local build of e.g.
# tests/s/mini/hello_macos_arm64.exe gets copied into the build
# context via COPY, and mk sees the target already up to date and
# skips its recipe -- silently masking recipe bugs (like a broken
# `if` as a recipe's last line) that a genuinely clean CI checkout
# would catch.
*.exe
*.uexe
